snippet.title: Dear Amber Hurd
snippet.description:
hello there and welcome back to the channel I know that I haven't been gone a while but the truth is that i miss uploading so I may be coming back more frequently! 

sorry for the rants recently I feel like it needs to be said and everything in this video is 100% accurate to the best of my knowledge, I was going to put something in hear about "don't take this to harshly" but I mean everything I said in that video and if your offended or on Amber Hurds side then DM me please thanks ;D and fuck you in advance 

DM me hear 
https://www.instagram.com/chris_king_3031/

thanks, 
Christopher King
